title: Routelay
body:
Project Description:
Digital payment solution; We accept fiat from customers and pay out crypto and vice versa; Think of us as Stripe or Razorpay for crypto or the DeFi & Blockchain community, we plan to add mAssets and provide specific support to the mStable dev community.

Funding Objective:
Provide a valid real world payment acceptance platform that can be integrated across any project in the world with special discounts. This will help in adoption of the mStable platform and provide a global presence.

Funding Schedule:
$50,000 USD immediately

Recipients Address:
0xc4f75cf3F89966930eE4dC2f6A47245104CFBD3e
